            "body": "> ... only mini.pick works because it's blocking and doing `vim.fn.getcharstr` in a loop.\n\nA little correction: it is explicitly *non-blocking* (other stuff still can happen behind the scene while picker is active), but it is *synchronous* (i.e. waits for user to select an item and returns it). That's why it works.",
